# Pitambari CMS / homepage + public QR (see USER_WEB_API.md in monorepo root).
#
# Canonical public website URL (https, no trailing slash). Used at build time for sitemap.xml + robots.txt.
# VITE_SITE_URL=https://www.pitambariindia.com
#
# Vite: `.env.production` is used only for `vite build`, NOT for `npm run dev`.
# The repo includes `.env` pointing at the live API. For dev with the local backend + proxy,
# add `.env.local` (gitignored): `VITE_API_URL=/api` (see vite.config.ts).
#
# Live API (HTTPS; `/api` is added in code if you omit it):
VITE_API_URL=https://api.pitambariindia.com
#
# Local backend without proxy:
# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:4000

# Rewards / loyalty server vars (see README.md) — separate from CMS.

# Contact form and patron reviews use `POST /api/v1/contact` and `POST /api/v1/reviews` (same API as above).
